                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div class="lg:hidden serif text-4xl md:text-5xl mt-20 mx-auto splitMeByLine">
                            Our collaborative process ensures the best ideas are brought to life—no matter who came up with them.
                        </div>
                        <div class="sans text-lg lg:text-xl mt-8 xl:mt-12 mr-6" data-sal="slide-down" data-sal-delay="400" data-sal-duration="800">
                            We are women- and minority-owned creative agency that builds pioneering work with our partners.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:col-9 hidden lg:block">
                    <h2 class="hero-h1 serif mt-4 xl:mt-12 lg:w-10/12 xl:w-7/12 mx-auto splitMeByLine">
                        Our collaborative process ensures the best ideas are brought to life—no matter who came up with them.
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

{% endif %}

